fields.name: Created
fields.description: The UTC date and time when the Transform was created, in 'YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ssZ' format.

fields.name: Description
fields.description: An optional verbose description of the Transform.

fields.name: LastModified
fields.description: The UTC date and time when the Transform was last updated, in 'YYYY-MM-DDThh:mm:ssZ' format.

fields.name: Outputs
fields.description: An array of one or more TransformOutputs that the Transform should generate.
